dump garbage on you

718
01:21:31,972 --> 01:21:32,939
You old fossil in white!

719
01:21:35,976 --> 01:21:36,943
Old fossil? Want to try me out?

720
01:21:40,981 --> 01:21:41,948
What did you call me?

721
01:21:54,995 --> 01:21:55,962
l'll have you sacked!

722
01:21:56,997 --> 01:21:58,965
She sure is a funny one!
- Enough

723
